subtitleNullable: Dataset regarding the games available on the Nintendo Switch Platform
descriptionNullable:
This is a Dataset Regarding the games available on the Nintendo Switch Console.
The data is sorted on the Total Sales of the games
The data was scrapped using Microsoft Excel from www.vgchartz.com .

**Column Description:**
- Position: This represents the position of the game based on total sales.
- Game: Name of the Game.
- Publisher, Developer:  The names of the Developer and Publisher.
- VGChartz Score, Critic Score, User Score: Ratings for the games based on various parameters.
- Total Shipped: Shows the total no.of units of the game shipped across the Globe.
- Release Date: Gives the release Date for the game.
- Last Update: Shows when the game was last updated.
